description: One of the most welcoming organizations I've attended. They were very supportive the whole time.
10 out of 10 would recommend, I made an error with my wallet and they showed a lot of integrity in helping me deal with this problem.
The organization was great, and had tools to support a wide range of people, however I think my specfic needs were not fully supported.
